	<context id="NewMapWizard">
		<description><b>New Map wizard</b>
Use this wizard to create a new map file. Create a map file if you want to configure a Mapping node using the Graphical Data Mapping editor.
You can also use this wizard to create a submap, which is a map file that is called from another map file instead of being called from a message flow node.</description>
	<topic href="../com.ibm.etools.mft.doc/cm28802_.htm" label="Creating a graphical data map"/>
	<topic href="../com.ibm.etools.mft.doc/br28800_.htm" label="Using graphical data maps"/>
	</context>
